snippet.textDisplay:
I'm not a superfan or anything, I don't know much about All Time Low or Alex, but what I got from this video was that Alex is a introverted person, or that he finds it hard to open up to others.


He went to this little meeting to try and fix that. When he was at the meeting he was friendly and people trusted him (eg. the trust fall). In the end, he helped everyone open up about their problems, which helped him feel better about himself. This is why it kept switching from the others to him during the last part of the video.


Through helping others open up, he was able to open up and tell them about his problems.


Ooooooor, it could be what everyone else thinks and what is probably right, he is just every one of those things and he's just singing about it.


Have a great day everyone! :D


P.S Most of that probably made no sense
